'''Copa de España de Fútbol Americano 2014''' (Spain's American Football Cup) was the 19th edition of the [[Spain's american football cup|Cup]].
Seven teams entered the competition. [[L'Hospitalet Pioners]] won the title for the fifth time in a row and ninth overall.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fefa.es/index.php?option=com_k2&view=item&id=267:pioners-consigue-su-noveno-t%C3%ADtulo-de-la-copa-de-espa%C3%B1a-ante-dracs-27-31&Itemid=102 |title=Pioners onsigue su noveno título de la Copa de España |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=8 December 2013 |website= fefa.es|publisher= |accessdate=10 December 2013}}</ref>
