{{use dmy dates|date=April 2015}} {{infobox country at games | NOC = HKG | NOCname = [[Sports Federation and Olympic Committee of Hong Kong, China]] | games = Summer Olympics | year = 1976 | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = {{url|www.hkolympic.org }}&nbsp;{{zh icon}} {{en icon}} | location = [[Montreal]] | competitors = 25 | sports = 6 | flagbearer = none | rank = | gold = 0 | silver = 0 | bronze = 0 | officials = | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = }}
'''[[Hong Kong]]''' competed at the '''[[1976 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Montreal]], Quebec, Canada. 25 competitors, 23 men and 2 women, took part in 27 events in 6 sports.<ref name="sports-reference">{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/HKG/summer/1976/ |title=Hong Kong at the 1976 Montreal Summer Games |accessdate=17 April 2015 |work=sports-reference.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417194704/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/HKG/summer/1976/ |archivedate=17 April 2015 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>
==Athletes== * [[Chan Fai Lui]] Cycling * [[Chan Lam Hams]] Cycling * [[Chan Wan Hei "Matthew"]] Fencing * [[Chow Tsun Man]] Shooting * [[Mark Anthony Crocker]] Swimming * [[Denis Cunningham]] Fencing * [[Reginald Dos Remedios]] Shooting * [[Hui Cheong]] Canoeing * [[Kam Wai Leung "Roger"]] Fencing * [[Kwan Honk Wai]] Canoeing * [[Lawrence Kwoh]] Swimming * [[Kwong Chi Yan]] Cycling * [[Lee Kui Nang "Solomon"]] Shooting * [[Raphaelynne Lee]] Swimming * [[Mak Chi Wai]] Canoeing * [[Mok Cheuk Wing]] Judo * [[Ng Hin Wan]] Canoeing * [[Ng Tsuen Man]] Canoeing * [[Ng Wing Biu]] Fencing * [[Camilo Pedro]] Shooting * [[Karen Robertson (swimmer)|Karen Robertson]] Swimming * [[Peter Rull, Sr.]] ([[Estonia]]) Shooting * [[Tang Kam Man]] Cycling * [[Tso Hok Young]] Shooting * [[John Wai]] Canoeing
