==Cycling== {{main|Cycling at the 1976 Summer Olympics}} Four cyclists represented Hong Kong in 1976.
;[[Cycling at the 1976 Summer Olympics – Men's individual road race|Individual road race]] * [[Kwong Chi Yan]] &mdash; did not finish (→ no ranking) * [[Chan Fai Lui]] &mdash; did not finish (→ no ranking) * [[Tang Kam Man]] &mdash; did not finish (→ no ranking) * [[Chan Lam Hams]] &mdash; did not finish (→ no ranking)
;[[Cycling at the 1976 Summer Olympics – Men's team time trial|Team time trial]] * [[Chan Fai Lui]] * [[Chan Lam Hams]] * [[Kwong Chi Yan]] * [[Tang Kam Man]]
;[[Cycling at the 1976 Summer Olympics – Men's 1000m time trial|1000m time trial]] * [[Chan Fai Lui]] &mdash; 1:16.957 (→ 28th place)
;[[Cycling at the 1976 Summer Olympics – Men's individual pursuit|Individual pursuit]] * [[Tang Kam Man]] &mdash; 24th place
==Fencing== {{main|Fencing at the 1976 Summer Olympics}} Four fencers, all men, represented Hong Kong in 1976.
;[[Fencing at the 1976 Summer Olympics – Men's foil|Men's foil]] * [[Ng Wing Biu]] * [[Kam Wai Leung]] * [[Chan Matthew]]
;[[Fencing at the 1976 Summer Olympics – Men's team foil|Men's team foil]] * [[Chan Matthew]], [[Denis Cunningham]], [[Kam Wai Leung]], [[Ng Wing Biu]]
;[[Fencing at the 1976 Summer Olympics – Men's épée|Men's épée]] * [[Kam Wai Leung]] * [[Denis Cunningham]] * [[Chan Matthew]]
;[[Fencing at the 1976 Summer Olympics – Men's team épée|Men's team épée]] * [[Chan Matthew]], [[Denis Cunningham]], [[Kam Wai Leung]], [[Ng Wing Biu]]
;[[Fencing at the 1976 Summer Olympics – Men's sabre|Men's sabre]] * [[Kam Wai Leung]]
