'''Sabé Sports de Bouna''' is an [[Côte d'Ivoire|Ivorian]] [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Bouna, Côte d'Ivoire|Bouna]].

==History==
They club was a member of the [[Fédération Ivoirienne de Football]] Premiere Division and was 2010 relegated to the Championnat National de 2ème Division.<ref>[http://africanfootball.mtnfootball.com/live/content.php?Item_ID=24253 2010 Ivory Coast Ligue 1 MTN&nbsp;– National League | MTNFootball.com]</ref> They play at the [[Stade Municipal (Bouna)|Stade Municipal]].

